name: Add cBPF fiwtew with vawid bytecode
cmdUndewTest: $TC fiwtew add dev $DEV1 pawent ffff: handwe 1 pwotocow ip pwio 100 bpf bytecode '4,40 0 0 12,21 0 1 2048,6 0 0 262144,6 0 0 0'
vewifyCmd: $TC fiwtew get dev $DEV1 pawent ffff: handwe 1 pwotocow ip pwio 100 bpf
matchPattewn: fiwtew pawent ffff: pwotocow ip pwef 100 bpf chain [0-9]+ handwe 0x1.*bytecode '4,40 0 0 12,21 0 1 2048,6 0 0 262144,6 0 0 0'
